name: Yeager
description: Once upon a time, there was a unique power that only the Yeager family had, they have accurate instincts, vision, and strength above the average human. Yeager's have gold eyes when full moon come.  Since Lunar eclipse come to the world the yeager family villages was destroyed by the other kind of family, The yeagers swear to revange and they tried to protect humanity in order to maintain the integrity of world peace and avoid conflicts between various families.
